abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastChannel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/88a65b6c-ab3c-4f01-ab3a-2c0640949ad7.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"The heartbeat-state.json is empty/disabled. I need to compare current state against the last known state from the previous cycle's messages.\\n\\nFrom the sessions_list at 07:15 UTC (last report time ~07:08 UTC based on the last Agent Status message), the state was:\\n- cron:ed2d0b5d (QLHV 5p): running ✅\\n- cron:e7885813 (Agent Status): running ✅ (but aborted last run)\\n- cron:6f3323ef (DTLX 5p): running ✅\\n- telegram:group:-5163901258: running ✅\\n\\n\\n- telegram:direct:6053576134: running ✅\\n- cron:53c5832a (Daily Briefing): done ✅\\n\\nNow checking the current state at 07:23 UTC: cron:ed2d0b5d is still running with active child sessions, cron:e7885813 is running but showing an aborted state with an error message, and cron:6f3323ef appears to be the same.\\n\\nThe main cron session itself is running. Telegram direct session has completed, while the group and other cron sessions remain stable. There are some orphaned cron sessions and failed subagent tasks from previous cycles, but those appear to be resolved. Most of the failed subagents are now complete, with just one remaining from the older batch.\\n\\nLooking at the broader picture, the cron:e7885813 abort is persistent across cycles and the Telegram session wrapping up is normal lifecycle behavior. The system state hasn't meaningfully shifted since the last check, so I'm keeping quiet about it.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"**No meaningful change since last cycle (07:08 UTC).** All stable:\\n\\n- `cron:ed2d0b5d` (QLHV 5p) — running ✅\\n- `cron:e7885813` (Agent Status) — running ✅ (pre-existing abort flag)\\n- `cron:6f3323ef` (DTLX 5p) — running ✅\\n- `telegram:group:-5163901258` — running ✅\\n- `telegram:direct:6053576134` — done ✅ (normal lifecycle completion)\\n- MCP: all healthy ✅\\n- Blockers: cron:ac986a8d + cron:b653a6c0 orphans (pre-existing, low priority)\\n\\n**Silent. No report sent.**\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 30620,\n            \"output\": 491,\n            \"totalTokens\": 45473,\n            \"cacheRead\": 13944,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 418,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776237849979,\n          \"responseId\": \"062e701bebb25c8ceb6f9bee38325428\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"ed1e0675\",\n            \"seq\": 5\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"origin\": {\n        \"provider\": \"telegram\",\n        \"accountId\": \"main_bot\"\n      },\n      \"displayName\": \"telegram:g-agent-master-orchestrator-telegram-direct-6053576134\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"telegram:6053576134\",\n        \"accountId\": \"main_bot\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1776237145658,\n      \"sessionId\": \"8e18daec-1780-455f-b7c4-896849ef86be\",\n      \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 67212,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0,\n      \"status\": \"done\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1776235606708,\n      \"endedAt\": 1776235626507,\n      \"runtimeMs\": 19799,\n      \"childSessions\": [\n        \"agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:8d8e1952-016d-4c2d-819c-c3b32e3b45