     \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"Now I have a full picture. Let me summarize for the Lead:\\n\\n**V4 Ecosystem Migration - Status:**\\n\\n✅ **Infrastructure (DONE):**\\n- 34 agent workspaces created\\n- Presence system (init/set/broadcast)\\n- SKILL_GATES.md for all 34 agents\\n- DEV_GATE.md for 5 key agents\\n- HANDOVER.md / FEEDBACK.md templates\\n- OPENSPEC_TRIGGER\\n- Ecosystem backup (2026-04-11)\\n- GIT_WORKFLOW.md (ecosystem standard)\\n- 17 commits ahead of origin/main (NEED PUSH)\\n\\n⚠️ **Pending Cleanup:**\\n\\n\\n- Project repos sitting in the v4-ecosystem-review workspace that should be relocated\\n- ops-manager directory partially cleaned up with remaining deleted files\\n- ahv-openclaw-setup package needs review for how it fits into the migration\\n\\nI should clarify with the Lead what they mean by \\\"plan migration\\\" — whether they're asking about the v4 infrastructure setup status or something else entirely.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"## V4 Ecosystem Migration — Status\\n\\n**Tổng quan:**\\n\\n| Hạng mục | Trạng thái |\\n|---|---|\\n| 34 agent workspaces | ✅ Hoàn tất |\\n| Presence system | ✅ Hoàn tất |\\n| SKILL_GATES / DEV_GATE | ✅ Hoàn tất |\\n| HANDOVER / FEEDBACK templates | ✅ Hoàn tất |\\n| Ecosystem backup | ✅ (2026-04-11) |\\n| GIT_WORKFLOW.md | ✅ Hoàn tất |\\n| **17 commits chưa push** | ⚠️ Cần push lên origin/main |\\n\\n**Chưa xong / Cần dọn dẹp:**\\n- Project repos (`ahv-qlhv-be`, `ahv-qlhv-fe`, `ahv-dtlx-backend`) nằm trong workspace v4-ecosystem-review — không đúng chỗ\\n- `ahv-openclaw-setup` — cần review xem có phải migration script chính thức không\\n- ops-manager: đã xóa nhưng chưa commit cleanup\\n\\n**Cần Lead xác nhận:** \\\"Plan migration\\\" ở đây là migration gì?\\n1. **V4 infrastructure** → ✅ gần xong, cần push