y wait — night silence is 23:00–07:00 UTC+7. Current time: 06:47 UTC = 13:47 UTC+7. That's AFTER 07:00 UTC+7, so it's not night time. But it's early morning. Per the rule: \"Reply HEARTBEAT_OK when: No active sessions AND current time is 23:00–07:00 UTC+7 (night silence)\".\n\n\nThe session count is 3, which means it's not night silence, so HEARTBEAT_OK applies. Since sessions are active and the time is past the quiet hours, there's nothing to flag here — just a routine heartbeat response."},{"type":"text","text":"HEARTBEAT_OK"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":2118,"output":208,"totalTokens":133992,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":131666,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776235693408,"responseId":"062e67afb00541e4edbd685d0d8eae0b","__openclaw":{"id":"b801d1b5","seq":197}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5163901258","kind":"group","channel":"telegram","origin":{"provider":"telegram","accountId":"main_bot"},"displayName":"telegram:g-ahv-qlhv-ecosystem","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram","to":"telegram:-5163901258","accountId":"main_bot"},"updatedAt":1776230490340,"sessionId":"8e0cb2bc-8245-4c89-bc2c-e3cca2257d0f","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":109097,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"running","startedAt":1776163408296,"endedAt":1776163783190,"runtimeMs":8014,"childSessions":["agent:senior-backend:subagent:f42cdd0e-8c76-42e7-ac2a-f1474568e0d4","agent:senior-frontend:subagent:cf1f74df-fd21-47ed-8a91-4c146aead234","agent:ui-ux-pro-max:subagent:469f1534-e128-44ea-af0d-73710c607372","agent:ui-ux-pro-max:subagent:ae038bd3-76fe-45b5-a5d7-b8797a299b2d"],"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","lastTo":"telegram:-5163901258","lastAccountId":"main_bot","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/8e0cb2bc-8245-4c89-bc2c-e3cca2257d0f.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Another heartbeat. Ack."},{"type":"text","text":"HEARTBEAT_OK"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":289,"output":14,"totalTokens":109111,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":108808,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776230479735,"responseId":"062e535265c30c7f2211a1ec73553a10","__openclaw":{"id":"9f731a62","seq":1248}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5168104492","kind":"group","channel":"telegram","origin":{"provider":"webchat"},"displayName":"telegram:g-5168104492","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram"},"updatedAt":1776226566166,"sessionId":"6381e723-5008-4cd7-8b2a-78406dd04d16","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":23865,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1776226512720,"endedAt":1776226564325,"runtimeMs":51605,"childSessions":["agent:prompt-optimizer:subagent:0eb3c914-87cc-4bdd-9ee9-20aa3e6473e1","agent:senior-backend:subagent:ce81d04d-cc26-4b7d-82f4-704a8256c73b","agent:senior-backend:subagent:e3ca11a2-c1e6-4d1d-9d7c-680d2d0d259a","agent:senior-backend:subagent:2e5ea409-572b-4929-8001-fa602be9c6d2","agent:senior-frontend:subagent:05e6701d-36aa-491c-ab9d-8edd7eeb37f8"],"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/6381e723-5008-4cd7-8b2a-78406dd04d16.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a full picture. Let me summarize for the Lead:\n\n**V4 Ecosystem Migration - Status:**\n\n✅ **Infrastructure (DONE):**\n- 34 agent workspaces created\n- Presence system (init/set/broadcast)\n- SKILL_GATES.md for all 34 agents\n- DEV_GATE.md for 5 key agents\n- HANDOVER.md / FEEDBACK.md templates\n- OPENSPEC_TRIGGER\n- Ecosystem backup (2026-04-11)\n- GIT_WORKFLOW.md (ecosystem standard)\n- 17 commits ahead of origin/main (NEED PUSH)\n\n⚠️ **Pending Cleanup:**\n\n\n- Project repos sitting in the v4-ecosystem-review workspace that should be relocated\n- ops-manager directory partially cleaned up with remaining deleted files\n- ahv-openclaw-setup package needs review for how it fits into the migration\n\nI should clarify with the Lead what they mean by \"plan migration\" — whether they're asking about the v4 infrastructure setup status or something else entirely."},{"type":"text","text":"## V4 Ecosystem Migration — Status\n\n**Tổng quan:**\n\n| Hạng mục | Trạng thái |\n|---|---|\n| 34 agent workspaces | ✅ Hoàn tất |\n| Presence system | ✅ Hoàn tất |\n| SKILL_GATES / DEV_GATE | ✅ Hoàn tất |\n| HANDOVER / FEEDBACK templates | ✅ Hoàn tất |\n| Ecosystem backup | ✅ (2026-04-11) |\n| GIT_WORKFLOW.md | ✅ Hoàn tất |\n| **17 commits chưa push** | ⚠️ Cần push lên origin/main |\n\n**Chưa xong / Cần dọn dẹp:**\n- Project repos (`ahv-qlhv-be`, `ahv-qlhv-fe`, `ahv-dtlx-backend`) nằm trong workspace v4-ecosystem-review — không đúng chỗ\n- `ahv-openclaw-setup` — cần review xem có phải migration script chính thức không\n- ops-manager: đã xóa nhưng chưa commit cleanup\n\n**Cần Lead xác nhận:** \"Plan migration\" ở đây là migration gì?\n1. **V4 infrastructure** → ✅ gần xong, cần push 17 commits + dọn repo\n2. **Migration script (ahv-openclaw-setup)** → đọc nội dung rồi báo cáo\n3. **Khác** → nói rõ hơn\n\nChờ Lead hướng dẫn tiếp."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":477,"output":565,"totalTokens":24430,"cacheRead":22455,"cacheWrite":933,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776226552335,"responseId":"062e43f9b5eb94d8ca5013359b1987c9","__openclaw":{"id":"6d34c150","seq":12}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:53c5832a-eecc-4d6b-a4c3-d1b78a430dca","kind":"other","channel":"unknown","label":"Cron: Daily Briefing 5AM UTC+7","displayName":"Cron: Daily Briefing 5AM UTC+7","updatedAt":1776208566543,"sessionId":"26f7c499-7fac-499e-bf9f-921a2e2ab1b6","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":21354,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"systemSent":true,"transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/26f7c499-7fac-499e-bf9f-921a2e2ab1b6.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have enough context. Let me compile the briefing.\n\nYesterday (2026-04-14):\n1. DTLX Backend Fix — `docs` vs `data` field mismatch fixed across all modules, 18/18 API endpoints verified ✅\n2. Pipeline degraded due to gateway timeout & Telegram delivery issues, but recovered to HEALTHY ✅\n3. Session cleanup — prior abort instances cleared ✅\n4. Students page filter bug fix ✅\n5. Cron jobs (5p progress + daily briefing) running ✅\n6. Telegram delivery instability resolved ✅\n\nToday (2026-04-15 in local time, but it's currently April 14 23:16 UTC = April 15 06:16 UTC+7):\n\n\nQLHV backend has a merge request pending Lead review, while AHV Works still needs P0 fixes and the Stitch MCP wrapper test plus stitch-connect skill update remain on the backlog. The pipeline is running clean with no active subagents, and both the DTLX backend and frontend are stable, though there's no current blocker aside from the QLHV BE MR awaiting review."},{"type":"text","text":"**DAILY BRIEFING — Orbis 🌐**\n📅 Tuesday, April 15, 2026 — 06:16 AM (UTC+7)\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n**STATUS: ✅ HEALTHY**\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n---\n\n**① YESTERDAY'S COMPLETED (Apr 14)**\n\n| # | Task | Status |\n|---|---|---|\n| 1 | DTLX BE Fix — `docs` vs `data` field mismatch | ✅ Fixed across all modules |\n| 2 | DTLX API Verification — 18/18 endpoints tested | ✅ All passing |\n| 3 | Pipeline Recovery — gateway timeout & Telegram delivery | ✅ HEALTHY restored |\n| 4 | Session Cleanup — prior abort instances cleared | ✅ Clean state |\n| 5 | Students page filter bug | ✅ Fixed |\n| 6 | Cron jobs (5p progress + daily briefing) | ✅ Running stable |\n\n---\n\n**② TODAY'S PRIORITIES (Apr 15)**\n\n| Priority | Task | Owner |\n|---|---|---|\n| 🔴 P0 | QLHV BE MR !6 — Lead review + merge | Lead |\n| 🟡 P1 | AHV Works — 13 P0 issues pending fix | Agent queue |\n| 🟡 P1 | Stitch MCP wrapper test | Agent queue |\n| 🟡 P1 | Update stitch-connect skill | Agent queue |\n\n---\n\n**③ BLOCKERS & RISKS**\n\n| Item | Status |\n|---|---|\n| Telegram delivery (17:40 UTC Apr 14) | ✅ Stable — no current issues |\n| QLHV BE MR !6 awaiting review | ⏳ Pending Lead action |\n| No active subagents | ✅ Zero overhead |\n\n---\n\n**System Summary:**\n- DTLX BE: Running port 5555 ✅\n- DTLX FE: Running port 3000 ✅\n- Pipeline: HEALTHY ✅\n- Active agents: 0\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n_Orbis 🌐 — 06:16 AM UTC+7_"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":527,"output":637,"totalTokens":21991,"cacheRead":14121,"cacheWrite":6706,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776208642698,"responseId":"062dfe0374f224e73bb8cb6eb49965ee","__openclaw":{"id":"311e7def","seq":7}}]},{"key":"agent:planner:subagent:ba49ac6d-ceff-4a9d-b3b1-7b89afdd88cc","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7","label":"5p-telegram-alert","displayName":"telegram:g-agent-planner-subagent-ba49ac6d-ceff-4a9d-b3b1-7b89afdd88cc","parentSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram"},"updatedAt":1776187887866,"sessionId":"30af124f-0456-4681-9d93-0475efdb80f2","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":11405,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1776187710991,"endedAt":1776187818978,"runtimeMs":6764,"thinkingLevel":"medium","abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/planner/sessions/30af124f-0456-4681-9d93-0475efdb80f2.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The subagent task is to send a specific message to a Telegram group. Let me check if there's a way to send Telegram messages through the available tools.\n\nLooking at the tools available, I don't see a direct Telegram sending tool. The tools available are:\n- read, edit, write, exec\n- process\n- sessions_list, sessions_history, sessions_spawn, sessions_yield\n- subagents\n- web_search, web_fetch\n- image\n- browser\n- memory_search, memory_get\n- Various confluence tools\n- Various gitlab tools\n- Various stitch tools\n- tts\n\nThere's no direct Telegram message tool. I should reply with the CANNOT_SEND format as instructed."},{"type":"text","text":"CANNOT_SEND: No Telegram messaging tool available in current toolset. Available tools do not include a Telegram send/post function."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":379,"output":172,"totalTokens":11577,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":11026,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776187812251,"responseId":"062daca5eb38f6849339f9f4c9083b45","__openclaw":{"id":"7b8fc739","seq":2}}]},{"key":"agent:planner:subagent:63bb70ce-b5f3-48d0-a236-b6cf5d8d7922","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7","label":"telegram-5p-status-v5","displayName":"webchat:g-agent-planner-subagent-63bb70ce-b5f3-48d0-a236-b6cf5d8d7922","parentSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1776185050306,"sessionId":"0ca2d212-43d7-42cb-a3eb-01e64cd33376","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":11258,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1776184755002,"endedAt":1776184856849,"runtimeMs":11708,"thinkingLevel":"medium","abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/planner/sessions/0ca2d212-43d7-42cb-a3eb-01e64cd33376.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The task is to send a specific message to a Telegram group. I need to use the `message` tool to send this message to the Telegram channel. Let me check the available tools... \n\nLooking at the tools, I don't see a direct `message` tool. But I see there's a `tts` (text-to-speech) tool. However, that won't send a Telegram message.\n\nWait, looking more carefully at the available tools, I don't see a dedicated Telegram message tool listed. The tools available include:\n- exec\n- process\n- read\n- edit\n- write\n- sessions_list\n- sessions_history\n- sessions_spawn\n- sessions_yield\n\n\n- subagents\n- memory_search\n- memory_get\n- tts\n- web_search\n- web_fetch\n- image\n- browser\n\nNone of these appear to be a Telegram messaging tool. Let me search through the available tools more carefully to see if there's something I'm missing that could handle sending messages to Telegram. I'm realizing I don't have access to a dedicated Telegram messaging tool in this environment—the available tools are primarily for browsing, file operations, and session management, none of which handle external messaging like Telegram. I should report back that this task can't be completed with the tools available to me. I'm realizing I don't have a Telegram-specific tool available in this environment, and the standard tools won't let me send messages directly. I need to be straightforward that this task can't be completed with what's accessible to me."},{"type":"text","text":"I don't have a Telegram messaging tool available in this environment. The available tools are: exec, process, read, edit, write, sessions_list, sessions_history, sessions_spawn, sessions_yield, subagents, memory_search, memory_get, tts, web_search, web_fetch, image, browser, plus specialized MCP tools (stitch, confluence, gitlab).\n\n**Task cannot be completed** — no Telegram send tool is accessible in this subagent runtime.\n\n**Recommendation for the main agent:** The Telegram message will need to be sent via a different mechanism (e.g., a dedicated Telegram bot runner, a cron/macro that calls the Telegram API directly, or a parent agent with the appropriate tool)."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":336,"output":448,"totalTokens":11706,"cacheRead":7447,"cacheWrite":3475,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776184845234,"responseId":"062da10dffbe4344ad63a1cddfb9e551","__openclaw":{"id":"8eaf43c5","seq":2}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:c2d275a5-d70a-4775-a268-fecf4708f133","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7","displayName":"telegram:g-agent-master-orchestrator-subagent-c2d275a5-d70a-4775-a268-fecf4708f133","parentSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram"},"updatedAt":1776184692752,"sessionId":"2514861e-9ccc-41ee-8f48-1e19d13c0819","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":11075,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1776184464031,"endedAt":1776184688954,"runtimeMs":16394,"thinkingLevel":"medium","abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/2514861e-9ccc-41ee-8f48-1e19d13c0819.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The main Orbis session is acknowledging the failure and will send directly. This subagent task is complete."},{"type":"text","text":"Roger that. Task acknowledged — Telegram delivery handled by Orbis main session.\n\n**Subagent Status:** ✅ Complete (no further action needed)"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":0,"output":53,"totalTokens":11128,"cacheRead":7305,"cacheWrite":3770,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776184684667,"responseId":"062da06d54b05398611ec226e7da423f","__openclaw":{"id":"f80ae44e","seq":4}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:b653a6c0-143b-4b53-a242-034bc5fd9